HEADWORD: Leitneriaceae
<hw>Leitneriaceae</hw> <pos>prop. n.</pos> <def>A natural family of
trees coextensive with the genus <gen>Leitneria</gen>; commonly isolated
in a distinct order.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> family Leitneriaceae, corkwood family.</syn>⟦br⟧
